#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:2
msgid "Extending the CLI"
msgstr "扩展 CLI"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:4
msgid ""
"LMCache's CLI is built on a plugin-style architecture that supports "
"**N-level nested subcommands** with zero-registration auto-discovery. "
"This guide explains how to add commands at each level."
msgstr "LMCache 的 CLI 基于插件式架构，支持 **N 级嵌套子命令**，并具有零注册自动发现功能。本指南解释了如何在每个级别添加命令。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:9
msgid "Architecture Overview"
msgstr "架构概述"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:11
msgid ""
"The CLI framework is composed of two core classes in "
"``lmcache/cli/commands/base.py``:"
msgstr "CLI 框架由两个核心类组成，位于 ``lmcache/cli/commands/base.py``："

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:14
msgid ""
"**BaseCommand** — Abstract base class for leaf commands (commands that "
"perform actual work)."
msgstr "**BaseCommand** — 叶命令的抽象基类（执行实际工作的命令）。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:16
msgid ""
"**CompositeCommand** — A ``BaseCommand`` subclass for commands that only "
"group sub-subcommands. It auto-discovers child commands by scanning the "
"package where it is defined."
msgstr "**CompositeCommand** — 一个 ``BaseCommand`` 子类，用于仅分组子子命令的命令。它通过扫描定义它的包自动发现子命令。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:20
msgid ""
"The discovery mechanism uses ``pkgutil.iter_modules`` to scan direct "
"submodules of a package, then collects all concrete ``BaseCommand`` "
"subclasses found in those modules. This means:"
msgstr "发现机制使用 ``pkgutil.iter_modules`` 扫描包的直接子模块，然后收集在这些模块中找到的所有具体的 ``BaseCommand`` 子类。这意味着："

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:24
msgid ""
"Each command is a separate ``.py`` file (or a sub-package with an "
"``__init__.py``)."
msgstr "每个命令都是一个单独的 ``.py`` 文件（或带有 ``__init__.py`` 的子包）。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:26
msgid ""
"No manual registration is needed — just create the file and it is picked "
"up automatically."
msgstr "无需手动注册 — 只需创建文件，它会自动被识别。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:28
msgid ""
"Utility/helper modules should be prefixed with ``_`` (e.g. "
"``_helpers.py``) so they are excluded from the scan."
msgstr "工具/辅助模块应以 ``_`` 为前缀（例如 ``_helpers.py``），以便在扫描时将其排除。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:32
msgid "Directory Layout"
msgstr "目录结构"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:55
msgid "Key Rules"
msgstr "关键规则"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:57
msgid ""
"A ``CompositeCommand`` subclass **must** be defined in the "
"``__init__.py`` of its package."
msgstr "一个 ``CompositeCommand`` 子类 **必须** 在其包的 ``__init__.py`` 中定义。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:59
msgid ""
"Modules starting with ``_`` are **excluded** from auto-discovery (use "
"this for helpers, utilities, internal logic)."
msgstr "以 ``_`` 开头的模块将 **被排除** 在自动发现之外（可用于助手、工具和内部逻辑）。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:61
msgid ""
"Each leaf command file should contain exactly one concrete "
"``BaseCommand`` subclass."
msgstr "每个叶命令文件应包含一个具体的 ``BaseCommand`` 子类。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:63
msgid ""
"The scan is **non-recursive** — each ``CompositeCommand`` only scans its "
"own package's direct submodules."
msgstr "扫描是 **非递归** 的——每个 ``CompositeCommand`` 仅扫描其自身包的直接子模块。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:67
msgid "Level 1: Adding a Top-Level Command"
msgstr "第 1 级：添加顶级命令"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:69
msgid "A top-level command appears directly under ``lmcache <command>``."
msgstr "顶级命令直接出现在 ``lmcache <command>`` 之下。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:71
msgid "**Step 1**: Create a new file under ``lmcache/cli/commands/``:"
msgstr "**步骤 1**：在 ``lmcache/cli/commands/`` 下创建一个新文件："

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:100
msgid "**Step 2**: Done! The command is automatically discovered. Test it:"
msgstr "**步骤 2**：完成！命令已自动发现。测试一下："

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:108
msgid ""
"This works because the top-level ``lmcache/cli/commands/__init__.py`` "
"calls ``discover_subclasses`` on its own package at import time. It uses "
"``pkgutil.iter_modules`` to find all direct submodules (files and sub-"
"packages), imports each one, and collects every concrete ``BaseCommand`` "
"subclass. The resulting list is stored in ``ALL_COMMANDS`` and registered"
" with the argument parser in ``main.py``. So adding a new ``.py`` file "
"with a ``BaseCommand`` subclass is all that is needed — no edits to any "
"other file."
msgstr "这之所以有效，是因为顶层的 ``lmcache/cli/commands/__init__.py`` 在导入时调用了其自身包中的 ``discover_subclasses``。它使用 ``pkgutil.iter_modules`` 查找所有直接子模块（文件和子包），导入每一个，并收集每个具体的 ``BaseCommand`` 子类。结果列表存储在 ``ALL_COMMANDS`` 中，并在 ``main.py`` 中与参数解析器注册。因此，只需添加一个带有 ``BaseCommand`` 子类的新 ``.py`` 文件即可——不需要编辑任何其他文件。"

