msgstr "**第 2 步**：在 ``__init__.py`` 中定义 ``CompositeCommand``："

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:150
msgid "**Step 3**: Add leaf subcommands as separate files:"
msgstr "**步骤 3**：将叶子子命令作为单独的文件添加："

