msgstr "级别 2：向现有组添加子命令"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:198
msgid ""
"If a ``CompositeCommand`` group already exists (e.g. ``bench``, "
"``quota``, ``trace``), you can extend it by simply adding **one new "
"file** — no other changes are required."
msgstr "如果已经存在一个 ``CompositeCommand`` 组（例如 ``bench``、``quota``、``trace``），您可以通过简单地添加 **一个新文件** 来扩展它——不需要其他更改。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:202
msgid ""
"For example, to add a new ``lmcache bench l2`` subcommand under the "
"existing ``bench`` group:"
msgstr "例如，要在现有的 ``bench`` 组下添加一个新的 ``lmcache bench l2`` 子命令："

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:205
msgid ""
"**Step 1**: Create a single file (or sub-package) in the existing group's"
" package directory:"
msgstr "**步骤 1**：在现有组的包目录中创建一个单一文件（或子包）："

