msgid "It does **not** start with ``_``."
msgstr "它\\ **不**\\ 以\\ ``_``\\ 开头。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:250
msgid "It contains a concrete ``BaseCommand`` subclass."
msgstr "它包含一个具体的 ``BaseCommand`` 子类。"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:253
msgid "Level N: Arbitrary Nesting"
msgstr "级别 N：任意嵌套"

#: ../../source/extension/cli.rst:255
msgid ""
"The framework supports **unlimited nesting depth**. Each level follows "
"the same pattern: a ``CompositeCommand`` in a package's ``__init__.py`` "
"auto-discovers its children."
msgstr "该框架支持 **无限嵌套深度**。每个级别遵循相同的模式：包的 ``__init__.py`` 中的 ``CompositeCommand`` 自动发现其子命令。"

